Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As times change, difficult cases\Nget more complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today marks the 2nd year of\NConan! He gets into big trouble fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Conan Edogawa Abduction Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me, "Eh?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since\Nyour parents transferred overseas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and left you here!\NDon't you miss them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What lousy parents! They don't\Nshow up even once, much less call!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! My lie's unraveling...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they really are overseas\Nright now, so it's not exactly a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it Professor Agasa\Nwho brought him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shouldn't we at least ask\Nhim how to contact his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? Is contacting them\Nbad or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not good! I gotta act quick\Nor they'll find out I'm Kudo Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Conan-{\i1}chan{\i0}!\NYou must've been lonely all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's alright, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! She's not your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear me! He's just being sulky,\Nafter being left alone all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Edogawa Fumiyo.\NEdogawa Conan's mother, in the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Edogawa Conan\Nis an alias I invented!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't possibly have parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate everything!\NI'll give you my thanks another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Send us\Na letter when you get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! Don't forget your thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I'm your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My mom is--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Your mother was a beautiful\NJapanese actress who enchanted men
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all over the world and won all the\Nmajor awards at the young age of 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she fell in love with\Nthe young novelist Kudo Yusaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,married at 20, and then simply retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She later had a son, but left\Nhim behind to travel the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Kudo Yusaku, now an\Ninternational-renowned mystery writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,\NKudo Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, their son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she with those men in black\Nwho shrunk me with their drug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still, and I'll take you to\Na nice place... A more fun place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What're you doing?! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone catch that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How? How did they find out who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it because I used\Nthe name "Kudo Shinichi"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the karaoke murder case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they heard from\Nsomewhere that I was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I told the inspector\Nnot to mention my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid! It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Kudo Shinichi? Should\NI go back and tell Ran everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they'd be in danger\Nif I go back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was careless. But it seems\Nthe boy really is Kudo Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. To think he really did shrink...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Look for him. It'll be\Na pain if he goes to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. His next destination\Nwill probably be "there"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa's House
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess my only choice is\Nto talk with Prof. Agasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since he knows the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's taking him so long?\NWhere is he wandering around now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?!\NSeems to be a kitchen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, my head's still swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I was carried into this\Nold house while I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You still haven't killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the orders from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that woman.\NAnd is that a man in front of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization wants him,\Nas an example of the drug's side-effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So that's why she didn't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that man is--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that masked man?!\NOh, crap! He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, is that really high\Nschool detective Kudo Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the day Kudo Shinichi\Nwent missing coincides
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the day that boy\Nappeared at that agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the crimes that happened\Naround him were solved easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can think of is\Nthat the drug really did shrink him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I try it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some of\Ntheir latest poison, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make someone take it, we can\Nfind out if it really shrinks people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who do we give it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man we're\Ndealing with tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the deal is done,\Nwe're supposed to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect chance to test the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we do find\Nout it shrinks people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we'll just kill the\Nman we're dealing with, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...snuff out the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to take him back\Nso they can investigate its side-effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't let\Npeople know its secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing things my way.\NDon't give me another corpse to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you tell the man\Nwhere tomorrow's deal is going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, using the usual method.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal is at 1:00 pm.\NGet sleep until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. They're both fast asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! He's sleeping with it on!\NTalk about creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I need to get these\Nropes off and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wine bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Wrap it in this mat and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Did they hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm in the clear.\NOkay! Now to use a shard to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Managed to get the rope off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but how do I get\Nout of this upstairs room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the snow,\Nit'd be too dangerous to jump out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess my only choice is\Nto hide in that fridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That wine must\Nbe dripping somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The kid's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He was gone when I got up!\NHe must've gone out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used the snow as a cushion\Nto get down! He's not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NLet's go find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. He's still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pretended to escape,\Nand is waiting for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Your hunch was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he has no place to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After today's deal,\Nwe'll find and eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure I was a goner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness I found this\Nstorage area beneath the mat then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Guess I'll look for\Nthat drug while I have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa said we could\Nfind a way to make me normal again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we figure out its composition...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he took\Nit all for today's deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this newspaper?\NIt has holes all over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've cut out\Nletters to make a message
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the guy they're dealing with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They said they're\Ngoing to kill that guy! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hafta find out where the deal is,\Nstop the murder, and get the drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guessing the missing letters\Ngives I, Te, Ho, Be, Ru, and Ka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rearranging them gives me "Beika Hotel"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beika Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't specify where in the hotel.\NAre any other letters missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck, none have been cut out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutter marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It was the August\Npage above it that was cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the August day\Nabove September 27th is... 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beika Hotel 30!"\NThat's where their deal is going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does "Beika Hotel 30" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel only has nineteen floors,\Nand there's no Room #30...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# 19? One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! It could be\Na baggage number! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daddy lost his number tag. It's #30...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# 30?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NWe only have up to #26...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! It's already past noon!\NAnd the deal is at 1:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I forgot my wallet in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did we park again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#42. Here's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the car parked on #30...\NCould the deal be happening in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no one inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing to our car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! He must be a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that! I just\Nthought it was a cool car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people seem\Ncompletely unrelated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's not here, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, a huge man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The parking space number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a small "1" written\Nin chalk next to the "30"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! "301" must be\Na room number at this hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's probably\Nthe guy they're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The masked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where\Nthey're making the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That masked man will kill me\Nfor sure if he catches me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?! What do I do?!\NWhat do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, Masao. The door locks by itself,\Nso you just need to close it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, be good while I'm gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:16:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! I'm not a bad guy!\NI'm Space Detective Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to catch evil\Naliens from Planet Ranpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply borrowing this\Nchild's form to deceive my foes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me your normal form!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait! I'm gonna\Ncall the cops on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Masao! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's my mommy's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Planet Ranpo!\NI can use any voice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's awesome!\NYou really are a space detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I managed to\Nfool him with this voice changer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is there any way I can help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is! For now,\NI'd like to use your phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and do you have any chewing gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I do! But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought your food and wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? We didn't order any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But we got a call earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I am feeling hungry.\NHave it brought in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! Bring it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum in the lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start with a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me first introduce\Nour other guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other guest?! Don't tell me\Nthat boy's under here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cart's a decoy.\NHe's really... inside this closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he get in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were talking\Nwith the bellboy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he put gum in the door\Nto defeat the automatic lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then snuck in while\Nwe were focused on the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think\NI'd fall for such a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! My only choice\Nis my Anesthetic Watch Gun--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had that interesting watch of\Nyours disabled after we caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret the day\Nyou underestimated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...high school detective, Kudo Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't tell? It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world-famous\Nmystery writer, Kudo Yusaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?\NThen don't tell me that lady is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact you couldn't tell means\NI still have the skills as an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that big guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mad!\NWe were worried too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Shin-{\i1}chan{\i0}! We stopped\Nby the house and you were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Prof. Agasa\Ntold you about how I shrank,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you cooked up this scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested your detective skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you successfully followed\Nall of our clues to make it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was just as I had\Ncalculated, until you were shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you knew I was hiding\Nin that kitchen's storage area?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Well, you just\Nbarely passed as a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's your own fault for\Nnot realizing I was dressed as
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Night Baron\Ncharacter from my novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! That was no time for that!\NI thought I was about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so? Well, what do you\Nsay we leave this dangerous country
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and live together leisurely overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Shin-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did this so you would\Nrealize the situation you're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I helped out\Nwith their act, Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have friends in the Interpol.\NI'll have 'em look into this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll get the drug at some point,\Nand you can be returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's put an end to this\Ndangerous detective game you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my case! I'll solve it!\NYou guys stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I can't afford\Nto leave Japan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NLet's humor him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the instant things get dangerous,\Nwe're taking you overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it seems you have other\Nreasons for not wanting to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving your son with us again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he insists on staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is his upbringing expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use however much of it you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'd be delighted\Nto take care of your adorable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and well-behaved son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Ran-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of him for me.\NIt seems he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Really, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dropping my manuscripts and\Nescaping to Japan was worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will Shin-{\i1}chan {\i0}be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll admit\Ndefeat sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you say\Nto a trip around the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the foreign magazine editors!\NHow'd they find me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call from your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now finish the last 308 pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped our presses!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can assume\Ndynamite was planted in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An act of tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.97,0:24:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This knife!\NRyoji was behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Three Hotta Siblings Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.62,0:24:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.52,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fertilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's culprit will truly surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:24:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss this year's Conan movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
